1.00	Riverfront_Theatre	Riverfront Arts Centre	The Riverfront (Welsh: ) is the principal and newest theatre and arts centre in the City of Newport, South Wales. It is located on the west bank of the River Usk on the Bristol Packet Wharf in the city centre. Designed by architect Austin-Smith:Lord, the centre was opened on 23 October 2004.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6c/Riverfront.JPG/300px-Riverfront.JPG
